name: WBTC
description:
Wrapped Bitcoin (WBTC) is the first ERC20 token backed 1:1 with Bitcoin.
Completely transparent. 100% verifiable. Community led.

name: JustCryptos
description: Just Cryptos builds a bridge that connects premium crypto currencies from the TRON network and other public chains, and introduces token value to TRON to power the JUST ecosystem. All assets are stored, and can be swapped on Poloniex.

name: Multichain
description: Cross-Chain Router Protocol (CRP), envisioned to be the ultimate router for Web3.

name: Poly Network
description: Poly Network is a global cross-chain protocol for implementing blockchain interoperability and building Web3.0 infrastructure. Poly Network has also integrated over 20 blockchains.

name: Portal
description: A token bridge built on Wormhole.

name: hBTC
description: HBTC token aims to promote the growth of the decentralized marketplace by injecting Bitcoin (BTC), the largest and most liquid asset, into the decentralized finance (DeFi) eco-system.

name: Orbit Bridge
description: Orbit Bridge is an interchain communication protocol that allows communication between heterogeneous blockchains. Through this, users can utilize the various assets of various chains in all dApps through simple transactions on each chain.

name: Synapse
description: Synapse is a universal cross-chain liquidity network. Synapse connects blockchains by offering an extensible cross-chain communication protocol that supports assets, smart contract calls, and more

name: ChainPort
description: ChainPort is a next-gen blockchain secure bridge that lets you hop across various blockchains at a click

name: cBridge
description: Celer cBridge is a multi-chain network that enables instant, low-cost and ANY-to-ANY value transfers within and across different blockchains, such as Ethereum and Polkadot, and different layer-2 scaling solutions on top, such as Optimistic Rollup, ZK Rollup and sidechains

name: Axelar
description: Axelar delivers secure cross-chain communication for Web3. Our infrastructure enables dApp users to interact with any asset or application, on any chain, with one click.

name: Terra Bridge
description: Terra Bridge enables cross-chain transfer of all tokens supported by Shuttle, including Terra native tokens, most mAssets and also other token types from Terra ecosystem.

name: Ad-Astra Bridge
description: Bridge between Ethereum and MultiversX

name: RelayChain
description: Access cross-chain opportunities on the World's Leading Blockchains using Relay's simple, fast, and secure bridge

name: ioTube
description: ioTube is the decentralized bridge for connecting Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, Polygon (Matic), and IoTeX. ioTube enables bi-directional exchange of tokens between IoTeX, Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, and now Polygon!

name: RenVM
description: An open protocol providing access to inter-blockchain liquidity for all decentralized applications. Bring BTC, BCH and ZEC to your Ethereum app.

name: Octus Bridge
description: Cross-chain transfers

name: tBTC
description: tBTC is Threshold's decentralized and permissionless bridge to bring BTC to the Ethereum network. tBTC has been designed to allow bitcoin holders to participate in Ethereum's Decentralized Finance (DeFi) applications. Users wishing to utilize their bitcoin on Ethereum can use the tBTC decentralized bridge to deposit their bitcoin into the system and get a minted tBTC token in their Ethereum wallet

name: Meter Passport
description: Meter Passport is a decentralized multichain bridge for the Meter ecosystem. Currently, it uses 3/5 multisig contract to secure the assets deposited on different chains. The relayers are independent professional staking service providers including protofire, hashquark, infinitystones, Wetez and Meter team. The Meter chain is used as the relay chain for the relayers to validate and vote on crosschain asset transfers and messages.

name: Injective Bridge
description: Access limitless DeFi markets with zero barriers.

name: Wan Bridge
description: Wanchain, the Wide Area Network chain, is the worlds premier decentralised blockchain interoperability solution.

name: NerveBridge
description: NerveNetwork is a Decentralized Digital Asset Service Network.It is an asset relay network connecting multiple blockchains, a completely gas-free blockchain.

name: Wrapped BNB
description: Wrapped BNB (BNB) is a Kava chain token that is backed 1:1 with BNB using the open BEP3 protocol. Completely transparent. 100% verifiable. Secured by Binance.com.

name: Allbridge
description: Allbridge is a simple, modern, and reliable way to transfer assets between different networks. It is a bridge between both EVM and non-EVM compatible blockchains, that aims to cover L2 solutions and NFT transfers in the future.

name: Hyphen
description: Hyphen provides simple APIs that lets you easily offer instantaneous value transfers between EVM chains, various L2s & allows quick onboarding from L1 to L2s.

name: XY Finance
description: XY Finance is One-Stop Cross-Chain Swap Aggregator for DeFi & Metaverse.

name: Interlay BTC
description: Fully trustless and decentralized Bitcoin bridge

name: deBridge
description: deBridge is a cross-chain interoperability and liquidity transfer protocol that allows the decentralized transfer of arbitrary data and assets between various blockchains

name: Strudel Finance
description: Strudel Finance provides the first one-way, trustless bridge linking Bitcoin and Ethereum.

name: SWFT
description: SWFT is a cross-chain swap aggregator for DEX/CEX/NFT.

name: DotOracle
description: DotOracle is a real-time decentralized Oracle and Cross-chain bridge supported by multi-chains such as Polkadot, Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, Fantom, Polygon, Avalanche, Tomochain, and Casper Network. It is currently the first cross-chain bridge on Casper Network and aims to support the Avalanche subnet.

name: Knit Finance
description: Developed Single infrastructure which will allow various assets , liquidity to move from one chain to another seamlessely as well enable liquidity staking for DPoS assets

name: Nomad
description: Nomad is an interoperability protocol for generalized message passing. We leverage an optimistic mechanism. There are no validators, and there is no blockchain. We're deployed as smart contracts between two chains, and has a lightweight off-chain component. This allows us to have less overhead and be more cost-efficient than other interoperability protocols.

name: CENNZnet Bridge
description: The bridge allows you to securely transfer tokens between CENNZnet and Ethereum.

name: Glitter Finance
description: Glitter Finance is a cross-chain, interoperability hub between the ecosystems of Algorand and Solana. More information can be found on glitterfinance.org

name: BridgeKek
description: Bridge from Ethereum Network to Kekchain.

name: Beamer Bridge
description: Enjoy Effortless Bridging - Beam your ERC20 assets between EVM-compatible rollups with certainty, speed and security.

name: Butter Network
description: Butter is set to change how users, projects, and dApps move tokens and NFTs between blockchains with a suite of proven-secure and user-friendly products

name: Lago Bridge
description: The Lago Bridge is the first bridge built on the Kadena blockchain. It is bi-directional and supports wrapping ERC-20 tokens to Kadena.

name: Printer Financial
description: Printer Financial is an EVM native cross-chain protocol that lets you transfer value seamlessly across chains and pays interest for providing liquidity. Rather than being pegged to a native token, PAPER is free to travel across all available chains at zero cost to you. No fee, no charge, no tax. Just the freedom to take your PAPER with you wherever you go in the blockchain.

name: anetaBTC
description: AnetaBTC is a fully on-chain, decentralized protocol that allows Bitcoin to be directly wrapped on the Ergo and Cardano blockchains. AnetaBTC enables Bitcoin holders to unlock the value of their assets in a secure and efficient environment to provide yield, without selling any Bitcoin and without any third-party custodian involvement.
